In [25]:
def diagnose(result):
    result.plot_diagnostics(figsize=(15,7))
    plt.show()
    
def actual_forecast(result,actual):
    pred=result.get_prediction(start=pd.to_datetime('1985-01-01'),dynamic=False)
    pred_ci=pred.conf_int()
    ax=actual['1985-01-01':].plot(label='observed')
    pred.predicted_mean.plot(ax=ax, label='Forecast', alpha=0.7, figsize=(14,7))
    ax.set_xlabel('Month')
    ax.set_ylabel('Sale')
    plt.title("Total Sale Forecast")
    plt.legend()
    plt.show()
    return pred_ci
